==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Camelot
<hw>Cam"e*lot</hw> <pr>(k⟦acr⟧m"⟦ucr⟧*l⟦ocr⟧t)</pr>, <pos>prop. n.</pos>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>The legendary site of <person>King Arthur's</person>
court and castle.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Hence, any place or time thought of as having
idyllic peace, justice, and happiness.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Camelry</ent>⟦br⟧
